    {
      "instruction": "<p>Coat the <strong>flattened steak[s]</strong> in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off the excess, then add them to the<strong> milk</strong> and then firmly press into the <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> to evenly coat all over</p><p>Tip: Make sure the steak[s] are fully coated in the breadcrumbs!</p>",
