    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the<strong> pork Tonkatsu</strong> finely and serve with the <strong>sticky</strong> <strong>rice</strong> and<strong> dressed slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>Tonkatsu-style sauce</strong> all over the sliced pork</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
